Redis client doesn't work in v4 of Redis. Replace the redisClient code with this:
let redisClient = redis.createClient({
    legacyMode: true,
    socket: {
        port: REDIS_PORT,
        host: REDIS_URL
    }
})

redisClient.connect().catch(console.error)

